                |  - Official documentation for domain migrations
              li
                a(href='https://search.google.com/search-console', target='_blank') Google Search Console
                |  - Monitor your migration progress and catch issues early
            
            p.mb-0
              | If you're thinking about a similar move, I'd say go for it. The benefits of having your own domain - better branding, consolidated SEO, and professional credibility - are definitely worth the effort.
              | Just make sure you plan it out properly, set up those redirects, and be patient while search engines process the change.
